init_text:
What Are the Most Important Things Students Should Learn in School?

In your opinion, what are the most important things students should learn in school? What is the most important thing you have learned in school? How has this knowledge affected your life? How do you think it will help your success in the future?

---

In my opinion,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I think that the most important thing I learned in school was how to learn new things.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This would allow for a hands-on approach to the concept of thinking critically and understanding how to apply it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As I got older, I learned the power of being able to freely think through problems and challenges that I encounter.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I don't have all the answers, however I can always figure out where to go to get them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: These subjects will help them to keep up, while also maintaining the ability to think for themselves.
